STATE
v.
RAMSEY 2018-1225 Supreme Court of Ohio. October 24, 2018

CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

MOTION AND PROCEDURAL RULINGS

On review of an order certifying a conflict. The court determines that a conflict exists. Sua sponte, cause held for the decision in 2018-0312, State v. Davis, and briefing schedule stayed.

Fischer and DeWine, JJ., dissent.
